{"tid":607034,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【不服來辯】講真足球要求嘅技巧一定多過藍波","createTime":"2018-03-27T02:58:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T08:12:34.000Z","uid":50727,"like":169,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"da59fc7d0e952b2acf378d465b65af3a3facdc8c","tid":607034,"uid":50727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T02:58:54.000Z","msg":"首先足球踢室外 落雨落雪大風少少都會影響成個比賽 每次起腳都要計埋有咩影響 藍波係室內高枕無憂中意點射都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟本唔需要技巧<br />\n<br />\n足球做防守嘅又要有速度又要夠硬淨去保護個波去同人爭 龍門又要反應快<br />\n<br />\n但相反藍波啲防守舉下手就算完全唔明有咩技巧 真係不知所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正評：一日玩具一世玩具<br />\n負評：明顯係玩具講技巧啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea02aaae6be30bac91d80d33f1b058b23373899","tid":607034,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:09:18.000Z","msg":"用腳，用手，完"},{"pid":"8c501d55382160a8a74f7b83c794e1bab0ffde48","tid":607034,"uid":160494,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"籃球"},{"pid":"c6f9f61359b4823cd594eb21ad7ccf20d56df7ac","tid":607034,"uid":50727,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c501d55382160a8a74f7b83c794e1bab0ffde48","tid":607034,"uid":160494,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T03:12:00.000Z","msg":"籃球"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:08:23.000Z","msg":"話之佢<br />\n咪又係玩具<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c5bbd863fd82f91da8e616c6a5aee7dc33160d","tid":607034,"uid":4578,"like":4,"dislike":23,"score":-19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:12:11.000Z","msg":"不了 人地個籃框咁細 你個龍咁大 <br />\n人地入波都多你唔知幾多倍 柒唔柒<img src=\"/ass